text: LA-5 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by the Waqar Ahmad Noor of Pakistan Muslim League (N). It covers the area of Barnala Tehsil in Bhimber District of Azad Kashmir, Pakistan. ==Election 2016== Category:Bhimber District Category:Government of Azad Kashmir Category:Constituencies of Pakistan
title: Constituency LA-5
